A set of MPI examples
---------------------

basics:
    - hello_world0
    - hello_world1
    - hello_world2

point-to-point communication:
    - hello_world3
    - mpi_send0
    - mpi_getcount0
    - mpi_sendrecv
    - mpi_buffer0
    - mpi_buffer1
    - mpi_buffer2
    - mpi_isend0
    - mpi_ringtopo
    - mpi_probe0
    - mpi_probe1
    - mpi_persistent0
    - mpi_persistent1
    - mpi_persistent2
    - mpi_persistent3

partitioned communication:
    - mpi_partitioned0
    - mpi_partitioned1

datatypes
    - predefined_datatypes
    - contiguous_ints
    - contiguous_struct
    - vector
    - vector_rowtype_fortran
    - vector_columntype_c
    - upper_triangular_matrix (indexed)
    - hvector
    - indexed
    - hindexed
    - indexed_block
    - hindexed_block
    - struct
